title: BRIEF-Coheris signs partnership with Orange
text:
BRIEF-Coheris signs partnership with Orange Sept 22 
Sept 22 Coheris SA : 
* Signs partnership with Orange SA to associate CRM offer and Business Analytics from Coheris with Flexible Computing Premium offer from Orange Business Services
